description: Looking for the finest food to cater your next special event? Then this is the perfect food truck for you! The BVSD School Food Project is not only providing excellent lunches to the many BVSD high schools, but also cooking up something fresh and fantastic to feed you and your guests. Sandwich platters, superb salads, and so much more are ready and waiting to make your day amazing!
name: BVSD School Food Project Food Truck
